data.description: This Sunflower model by Westbay homes was perfectly designed to enjoy its open floorplan and abundant natural lighting... From your first step inside the front door, you will be impressed with Westbay's attention to detail and beautiful design features.. The chef's kitchen includes a large center island with stunning stone counters, 42" upper cabinets, stainless steel appliances, glass tile backsplash, and a walk-in pantry. Your gorgeous kitchen shares the same massive space with your oversized dining area and family room. The downstairs bedroom/guest suite is tucked away just beyond the kitchen and offers a perfect space and full hall bath for visiting family and friends. Upstairs you'll find your oversized loft that's a perfect place for relaxation, a play space, or office... Retire every evening to your spacious primary suite with sitting area and ensuite bathroom with dual sinks and large walk in closet. Your two additional upstairs bedrooms are large in size with ample closet space! Your convenient upstairs laundry room has plenty of room for your washer/dryer and storage galore! Outside, enjoy your morning coffee or evening night cap on your screened in lanai. Last, but certainly not least, is the attached, rear entry two-car garage. Your driveway is so long you'll have plenty of room for multiple vehicles... Hosting a party or family gathering? There are multiple extra parking spots just north of your home so your quests will NEVER have issues finding a place to park!! The community itself is highly desired for its amazing amenities. Featuring a pool, clubhouse, tennis and basketball courts, a dog park, fitness center, and sits on a 1,200 Acre Preserve with of hiking trails, over 18 miles Of mountain bike trails! This community has anything you could ever want!
